Tired of the way your Home Screen looks and want something new? Refresh it with our brand-new Aesthetic App Icons & Themes for every taste, color and mood! Make your Home Screen unique!

X Icon Changer App Content & Main Features:
– Theme Gallery – explore 20 categories of unique Themes, such as: Neon, Luxury, etc;
– Themes Preview – see how the selected Theme will look on Home Screen before adding it on your own;
– Icon Maker – create your own app icons by adding a frame or your photo to the background, picking colors for the icon and background, zooming and rotating icon. Contains 1250+ Icons and 220+ Frames to choose from;
– 35,000+ App Icons with weekly updates;
– 200+ Themes with weekly updates;
– No ads!

Each theme contains resources for saving and setting, such as: 
– 181 App Icons;
– 1 Wallpaper.

These icons are for custom shortcut using the “Shortcuts” app. Please note that they don’t change your current app icons.

How to Add Icons to your Home Screen?
1. Open ”Shortcuts” App;
2. Tap the Add (“+”) button in the upper-right corner;
3. On the New Shortcut screen, tap on “Add Action”;
4. Tap on “Scripting”;
5. Tap on “Open App”;
6. Tap on “Choose”;
7. Find and select the app you want to change icon;
8. Tap on the Three Dots (•••) in the upper-right corner;
9. Tap on “Add to Home Screen”;
10. Enter the name of app icon;
11. Tap on the icon, then “Choose Photo” and choose from your Photos the icon you want to set;
12. Tap on the “Add” button in upper-right corner;
13. Done! Just select the position for the icon on your custom home screen.

Unclear? Do not worry! You can find a more detailed guide with pictures inside the app by clicking on the ( i ) button.

* Note: Free version of the app is limited to 20 Themes only (1 Theme for Free in each category). If you want to use the app without limits, an auto-renewable subscription ”X Icon Changer Pro” is available.

